    "text": "Totally 228 alleles were detected, with an average of 6.16 alleles per locus. The polymorphism information content (PIC) value for each locus ranged from 0.413 to 0.847, with an average of 0.697. A positive correlation was found between PIC and number of alleles and between PIC and number of repeat unit [0.802 and 0.429, respectively (P < 0.01)].",
